=== 食用 ===
荨麻叶浸泡后可以去除其毒性食用，尤其是嫩芽非常可口，适宜作汤或作为[[蔬菜|蔬菜]]，用[[荨麻汤|荨麻汤]]在北欧尤其流行。除了煮湯，也可以混入麵食或乳酪，例如[[康沃爾·雅格芝士|康沃爾·雅格芝士]]。與其他蔬菜相比，蕁麻算是非常營養的蔬菜，富含有[[維生素A|維生素A]]、[[維生素C|C]]、鐵、鉀、鎂、鈣，尤其蛋白質含量可達乾重的四分之一<ref>{{cite journal|doi=10.1002/jsfa.2740311210|title=The dietary potential of the common nettle|year=1980|last1=Hughes|first1=R. Elwyn|last2=Ellery|first2=Peter|last3=Harry|first3=Tim|last4=Jenkins|first4=Vivian|last5=Jones|first5=Eleri|journal=Journal of the Science of Food and Agriculture|volume=31|issue=12|pages=1279–86|pmid=6259444}}</ref>。開花後在葉肉中產生{{link-en|鐘乳體|cystolith}}，不適合食用。英國[[多塞特郡|多塞特郡]]從1986年起有一吃蕁麻比賽，參賽者比賽在有限時間內誰能生吃最多蕁麻<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/dorset/content/articles/2005/06/17/nettle_eating_feature.shtml|title=World nettle eating championships|work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=17 June 2005|accessdate=3 July 2012|archive-date=2022-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220405044041/https://www.bbc.co.uk/dorset/content/articles/2005/06/17/nettle_eating_feature.shtml}}</ref><ref>Langley, William. (14 June 2009) [https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/howaboutthat/5525806/World-Stinging-Nettle-Eating-Championship-attracts-record-crowd.html World Stinging Nettle Eating Championship attracts record crowd] {{Wayback|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/newstopics/howaboutthat/5525806/World-Stinging-Nettle-Eating-Championship-attracts-record-crowd.html |date=20210518130754 }}. ''[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]'' (London). Retrieved on 3 July 2012.</ref>。

=== 药用 ===
荨麻的药用是作为一种催乳剂<ref>Westfall R.E., Galactagogue herbs: a qualitative study and review. Canadian Journal of Midwifery Research and Practice. 2(2):22-27. (2003)</ref>，曾经试验用荨麻的叶汁作为慢性鬱血性心衰竭病人的利尿剂。

民间偏方用荨麻刺激皮肤可以缓解风湿病造成的痛苦。荨麻制剂可以止痛、用于治疗[[关节炎|关节炎]]、[[贫血症|贫血症]]、干草热可[[肾脏|肾脏]]疾病。用在洗发液中可以防止头皮屑<ref>Balch, Phyllis A., CNC, Balch, James F., M.D., Prescription for Nutritional Healing, Avery Press, p. 104 (2000) (ISBN 1-58333-077-1)</ref>，据说还可以医治[[湿疹|湿疹]]。

荨麻根的提取物曾试验用于良性[[前列腺|前列腺]]增生治疗<ref>Lopatkin N, Sivkov A, Walther C, Schlafke S, Medvedev A, Avdeichuk J, Golubev G, Melnik K, Elenberger N, Engelmann U. Long-term efficacy and safety of a combination of sabal and urtica extract for lower urinary tract symptoms: a placebo-controlled, double-blind, multi-center trial. ''World Journal of Urology''. 2005 June 1</ref>。

由于鲜荨麻叶含有高浓度的[[维生素K|维生素K]]，民间用其在受伤时止血。

可作為利尿劑、去痰劑、止痛劑和滋補劑。對於良性前列腺增生、貧血、關節炎、風濕病、乾草熱、其他過敏性的疾病、腎臟疾病和吸收不良症候群有益。改善甲狀腺腫、發炎情況和肺部黏液情形。用於頭髮的保養產品上，有助於刺激頭髮毛囊和調節頭皮油脂的聚集。

